    corresponding point of <i>vector</i>.
    </dl>

    <a name="sum"></a>
    <dl>
    <dt><b>sum function</b>: <tt>sum</tt>(<i>vector</i>)<dd>
    This function returns the (scalar) sum of the elements of
    <i>vector</i>.
    </dl>

    <a name="tan"></a>
    <dl>
