    variable is set to "<tt>degrees</tt>".
    </dl>

    <a name="tanh"></a>
    <dl>
    <dt><b>tanh function</b>: <tt>tanh</tt>(<i>vector</i>)<dd>
    Each point of the returned vector is the hyperbolic tangent of the
